---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Resources — EP Docs">
  <h1>Resources</h1>
  <p>
    A curated collection of tools and resources to help you create an outstanding Engineering Portfolio.
    Use these resources to learn more about other portfolios and gain insights about your own, but remember — the best portfolios reflect your team's unique journey.
  </p>

  <section class="resource-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <h2>Traditional Tools</h2>
        <p>Classic, reliable tools that don't rely on AI — full control over your content.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Design & Layout</h3>
    <div class="resource-grid">
      <a href="https://www.canva.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>Canva</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Design</span>
          <p>Free, easy-to-use design tool with templates. Great for teams without design experience.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.figma.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>Figma</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Design</span>
          <p>Professional design tool with collaboration features. Steeper learning curve but more powerful.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="resource-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <h2>Learning Resources</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="resource-grid">
      <a href="https://portfolioperch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>Portfolio Perch</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Guide</span>
          <p>A collection of 75+ portfolios created between 2020 and 2023.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.ftcportfoliolab.org/portfolio" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>PortfolioLab</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Guide</span>
          <p>Nearly 40 portfolios made in the past 6 years.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.open-vault-ftc.org/portfolios/portfolios" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>Open Vault</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Guide</span>
          <p>A collection of 100+ portfolios from the 2023-2024 season.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="resource-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <h2>AI-Powered Tools</h2>
        <p>These tools use artificial intelligence to assist with writing, design, and organization.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout warning">
      <strong>Important:</strong> Always verify AI-generated content for accuracy. Use AI as a starting point, 
      not a final product. All competitions require portfolios to represent <em>your team's</em> authentic work.
      <strong>Do not attempt to use AI to create your portfolio.</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="resource-grid">
      <a href="https://coach.team31000.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>FTC Coach</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Feedback</span>
          <p>Designed by Vanta Robotics, this tool takes your portfolio and evaluates your award potential, layout, and design on a scale of 0-100.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.grammarly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-info">
          <h3>Grammarly</h3>
          <span class="resource-tag">Writing</span>
          <p>AI-powered grammar, spelling, and style checker. Helps maintain professional writing quality.</p>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .resource-section {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .section-header > div > p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .resource-section h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .resource-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .resource-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .resource-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .resource-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .resource-info {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .resource-info h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
  }

  .resource-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .resource-info p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .resource-card > svg {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .resource-card:hover > svg {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translate(2px, -2px);
  }

  .callout {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .callout.warning {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .callout.warning {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .resource-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .section-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .resource-card {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    }

    .callout {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
